# EXIT STRATEGY (STABILIZED 2026-04-16)

## Berechnungsformel (live-paper-trading-v4.ts:1485-1515)

```typescript
// STABILIZED EXIT STRATEGY (2026-04-16)
// SHORT Position: PnL = (entryPrice - currentPrice) / entryPrice

let shouldExit = false;
let exitReason = '';

// Take Profit: +15% (realistic for memecoins)
if (pnlPercent > 0.15) {
  shouldExit = true;
  exitReason = 'TAKE_PROFIT_15%';
}

// Stop Loss: -5% (ALWAYS ACTIVE - no exploration mode bypass!)
else if (pnlPercent < -0.05) {
  shouldExit = true;
  exitReason = 'STOP_LOSS_5%';
}

// Time-based Exit: 4 hours max
else if (holdingHours > 4) {
  if (pnlPercent > 0) {
    shouldExit = true;
    exitReason = 'TIME_PROFIT_4H';
  } else {
    shouldExit = true;
    exitReason = 'TIME_STOP_4H';
  }
}
```

## WICHTIG: Exploration Mode ist DEAKTIVIERT

```typescript
// DIESER CODE EXISTIERT NICHT MEHR!
// if (!isExplorationMode && pnlPercent < -0.08)
// Stop-Loss ist jetzt IMMER aktiv!
```

