# CRASH DETECTION METRICS

## Die 9 Metriken (alle aktiv)

| Index | Name | Schwellenwert | Richtung |
|-------|------|---------------|----------|
| n | Hawkes Normalization | > 0.8 | HIGH = gefaehrlich |
| PE | Price Entropy | < 0.35 | LOW = gefaehrlich |
| kappa | Molloy-Reed Index | < 3.0 | LOW = gefaehrlich |
| fragmentation | Market Fragmentation | > 0.7 | HIGH = gefaehrlich |
| rt | Epidemic Rt | > 1.2 | HIGH = gefaehrlich |
| bValue | Gutenberg-Richter b-value | < 1.0 | LOW = gefaehrlich |
| CTE | Cluster Transfer Entropy | > 0.6 | HIGH = gefaehrlich |
| SSI | Super-Spreader Index | > 5.0 | HIGH = gefaehrlich |
| LFI | Liquidity Flow Index | > 2.0 | HIGH = gefaehrlich |

## Zone Thresholds (live-paper-trading-v4.ts:714-715)

```typescript
if (crashProb >= 0.15) zone = 'IMMEDIATE_SHORT';   // >= 15%
else if (crashProb >= 0.12) zone = 'MONITOR';      // >= 12%
else zone = 'IGNORE';
```

| Zone | Crash Probability | Aktion |
|------|-------------------|--------|
| IGNORE | < 12% | Kein Trade |
| MONITOR | 10% - 15% | Beobachten |
| IMMEDIATE_SHORT | >= 15% | Moeglicher Short |

