# BAYESIAN DECISION ENGINE

## makeDecision Logik (bayesian-decision-engine.ts)

```typescript
// Entscheidung erfordert ZWEI Bedingungen:
// 1. Zone = IMMEDIATE_SHORT (crashProb >= 15%)
// 2. Posterior >= 0.5 (Bayesian Konfidenz)

if (crashSignal.zone === 'IMMEDIATE_SHORT' && posterior >= 0.5) {
  return { action: 'SHORT', ... };
} else if (crashSignal.zone === 'MONITOR' || (posterior < 0.5 && crashProb >= 0.08)) {
  return { action: 'MONITOR', ... };
} else {
  return { action: 'IGNORE', ... };
}
```

