# LIGHTGBM TRAINING DATA PIPELINE

## Gesammelte Features (pro Cycle)

| Kategorie | Features | Beschreibung |
|-----------|----------|---------------|
| Identifikation | timestamp, slot, cycleNumber, symbol | Zeitstempel und Symbol |
| 9 Roh-Metriken | n, PE, kappa, fragmentation, rt, bValue, CTE, SSI, LFI | Unveränderte Crash-Metriken |
| 9 Z-Scores | z_n, z_PE, z_kappa, z_fragmentation, z_rt, z_bValue, z_cte, z_ssi, z_lfi | Normalisierte Metriken für ML |
| Bayesian Output | crashProbability, zone, confirmingMetrics | Model Output |
| Bot Detection | botProbability, jitoBundleCount, sandwichCount, sniperCount, liquidationCount, arbitrageCount, backrunCount, highPriorityTxCount, veryHighPriorityTxCount, avgFee | Bot-Aktivität |
| Order Flow | tfi, tfi_pressure, buyVolume, sellVolume, volumeRatio | Handelsfluss |
| Velocity | priceChange1min, priceChange5min, acceleration, jerk, isFlashCrash | Preisdynamik |
| Trade Outcome | tradeAction, tradeReason, pnlSol, pnlPercent, holdingHours | **LABELS für Training** |

## Datenspeicherung

```
/data/trinity_apex/solana-stream/paper-trading/logs/lightgbm/
```

Format: JSONL (eine Zeile pro Cycle)

## Labeling Strategy

1. **PENDING**: Prediction erstellt, 24h Window läuft
2. **TRUE_POSITIVE**: Short eröffnet + Preis DROP >= 3%
3. **FALSE_POSITIVE**: Short eröffnet + Preis STAY/STEEIG
4. **TRUE_NEGATIVE**: IGNORE Zone + kein Crash in 24h
5. **FALSE_NEGATIVE**: IGNORE Zone + doch Crash in 24h

